{
  "texts": [
    "A similar procedure was followed to study BOLD signals inside the lesioned tissue.",
    "For each patient, the binary mask containing the edema was used to extract the time series from the patient, as well as from all control subjects.",
    "Consequently, BOLD signals in lesioned regions of the brain were comparable to 11 healthy signals from the same region.",
    "No network was computable in this case, making the use of Eq.",
    "(2) pointless."
  ]
}